OL,5,EEMULATORSBNo one is quite sure whether 
OL,6,Bemulators - programs which "emulate"   
OL,7,Bthe software of another machine, and   
OL,8,Ballow you to play its games on your PC,
OL,9,Bor whatever - are illegal or not.      
OL,11,BIs it breach of copyright to use an    
OL,12,Bemulator to play games which are no    
OL,13,Blonger profitable? We cannot say.      
OL,15,BIt doesn't really matter, though.      
OL,16,BEmulators aren't designed for ease of  
OL,17,Buse - only nerdoid brainiacs can get   
OL,18,Bthem up and running.                   
