OL,5,EETERNAL CHAMPIONSBA Mega Drive beat 'em
OL,6,Bup developed by Sega. Curiously, former
OL,7,Bindustry figurehead Julian "Jaz"       
OL,8,BRignall gave the game 96% and declared 
OL,9,Bit "better than Street Fighter 2" in   
OL,10,Bhis review for Mean Machines.          
OL,12,BWhere is it now, eh? More importantly, 
OL,13,Bwhere is HE now? In California, earning
OL,14,Blots of money for Virgin, we believe.  
OL,16,EEARTHWORM JIMBClassic 16-bit           
OL,17,Bplatform game. Confused everyone       
OL,18,Bbecause the Mega Drive version was     
OL,19,Bbetter than the SNES incarnation.      
