OL,4,G                                       
OL,5,EE3BThe Electronic Entertainment Expo.  
OL,6,BA recent phenomenon, America's E3 show 
OL,7,Bhas replaced the Consumer Electronics  
OL,8,BShow as the centerpiece of the video   
OL,9,Bgames industry's year.                 
OL,11,BSuffice to say, it's exactly the same  
OL,12,Bas the European Computer Trade Show,   
OL,13,Bbut 100 times more expensive to get to.
OL,15,BThis year's show was alternately       
OL,16,Bdescribed as "The best yet" and "A     
OL,17,Bwaste of time" by visitors. It'll be   
OL,18,Bthe same story after ECTS.             
